{"tid":2424234,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港台電視31]鏗鏘說 逢星期五 2000-2030","createTime":"2021-02-26T12:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:13:04.000Z","uid":30294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f4181c57a5494ff8433354ca8f581964101f479f","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:03:37.000Z","msg":"《鏗鏘說》是屬於人物專訪節目，由一位嘉賓主持訪問一位嘉賓，透過兩人觀看《鏗鏘集》歷年精選的作品片段，從中分享兩人的經歷、感受和成長故事。既透過重溫紀錄片的時化變遷，也透過訪談，道出主持和嘉賓的人生故事和意見觀點。紀錄片穿插人物專訪，互相扣連。<br />\n<br />\n【鏗鏘說新一季】沈祖堯：「香港，永遠是我深愛的家」。<br />\n被稱為「沙士英雄」的中大前校長沈祖堯，即將離開香港。離開前夕，他分享了他對香港，中文大學這兩個「家」的懷緬及展望未來的生活。由沙士抗疫搶救醫護同事的故事，說到朱咪咪如何令他踏上校長之路。<br />\n《鏗鏘說：瘟疫蔓延時》<br />\n今晚八點港台電視31<br />\n主持：碧樺依<br />\n#鏗鏘說<br />\n#沈祖堯<br />\n#碧樺依<br />\n<br />\n【鏗鏘說新主持】做《鏗鏘說》主持，不但要問，也要聆聽。新主持之一的碧樺依，把她社工訓練的同理心，應用在主持工作上。<br />\n碧樺依曾被稱為社福界「女神」，她巴基斯坦混血兒身份亦經常被談論，她說，社會要打破這種標籤和刻板印象，放開偏見去認識一個人。《鏗鏘說》讓她看到一個公眾人物，鏡頭後更多真實的一面和故事。<br />\n她現在中大任教，新一季《鏗鏘說》第一集，就由她訪問前中大校長沈祖堯，在熟悉的校園發掘他的另一面。<br />\n#鏗鏘說<br />\n#新主持<br />\n#碧樺依<br />\n#女神<br />\n#種族平等議題"},{"pid":"fac3e98d1bdb6cf1573ac491eed069adcd106a72","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"被稱為「祖堯BB」的前中大校長沈祖堯在訪問中說, 當年和朱咪咪一次上台表演, 令他踏上校長之路。這位「沙士英雄」以往專注在醫學上,做校長令他開拓了新思維。他即將離港,亦期望接受新挑戰。<br />\n《鏗鏘說：瘟疫蔓延時》<br />\n全集重溫：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K3FDCOpMPsQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK3FDCOpMPsQ&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2By%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=8fbc0aaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K3FDCOpMPsQ</a><br />\n#鏗鏘說<br />\n#沈祖堯<br />\n#碧樺依"},{"pid":"e3080470df1b41f2cb876858ed64542b1cac772c","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/152935672_3689474131101642_305630374721470143_n.png?_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=3&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=Ft_W-u0u7woAX_14blc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=4ab3d42b4c83db66b9c90ff703f832e2&amp;oe=605E0700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F152935672_3689474131101642_305630374721470143_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26ccb%3D3%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DFt_W-u0u7woAX_14blc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3D4ab3d42b4c83db66b9c90ff703f832e2%26oe%3D605E0700&h=ca0e3272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【鏗鏘說新主持】出身於友台，並一直擔任DJ的黃志淙，加入主持港台《鏗鏘説》，超越平台，貫徹他一向跨界別風格。他是樂評人，文化人，創作人，主持，老師⋯⋯擁抱多元，視野廣闊。<br />\n志淙的工作大部份和音樂和文化有關，最廣為人熟悉的Chi Chung&rsquo;s Choice, 推介歐美流行音樂，陪伴一代年青人成長。今次主持人物訪談節目，既是新挑戰，也跨進不同嘉賓的領域，發掘新故事。<br />\n新一季《鏗鏘説》第二集，志淙訪問岑寧兒，不只說音樂，也一起談香港這個「家」。星期五晚八點港台電視31。<br />\n#鏗鏘說<br />\n#新主持<br />\n#黃志淙<br />\n#跨領域文化人<br />\n#第二集<br />\n#岑寧兒"},{"pid":"948cfacac878eab008c7e76a09626b42e668bc95","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"【鏗鏘說】第二集嘉賓岑寧兒。生於香港，中學畢業後到加拿大讀書； 在北京遇上恩師，後來獨闖台灣發展音樂事業。因為疫情，她意外地留在香港一段較長時間，意外地認真思考起「哪裡是家？」的問題。她有了答案⋯⋯在《鏗鏘說》和我們分享。今晚八點聽她說。<br />\n《鏗鏘說：常願意。回家》<br />\n今晚八點港台電視31<br />\n主持：黃志淙<br />\n#鏗鏘說<br />\n#岑寧兒<br />\n#黃志淙"},{"pid":"b8a8e4b4a47f9ea0185c4ae9b881bd80c2210142","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"見冇人開所以我開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859543e9101185f6b0510514c557ad9acb895ab9","tid":2424234,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"睇緊 viutv 🙂"},{"pid":"f057cc0bffe5d55f09d8d45e1a7cd1c2e6d4c2a8","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"859543e9101185f6b0510514c557ad9acb895ab9","tid":2424234,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"睇緊 viutv 🙂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"之前黃viu睇哂了"},{"pid":"849202b1e372881443f4ebd06efb701e8eda9b26","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"ChiChung訪問岑寧兒夠哂份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679b1a6a11e09b564b5f3c215d3744a5cacd5292","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:20:29.000Z","msg":"有d羡慕佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bb49f474d3f1eb751c04eb3073879f8a4bd221","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:28:11.000Z","msg":"把聲真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a23851f30baf9715a8aff8acaada61cd92b42c7","tid":2424234,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"睇緊31台 yoyo 不如去台灣啦"},{"pid":"2d1de653d0a3c0581b94523bd02eaad27b841b64","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a23851f30baf9715a8aff8acaada61cd92b42c7","tid":2424234,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"睇緊31台 yoyo 不如去台灣啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:33:25.000Z","msg":"佢係台灣地位好高"},{"pid":"14e8374462725c1787adb04f79c885b78a82908a","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T12:01:21.000Z","msg":"【鏗鏘說】三八婦女節快到，今集嘉賓現任婦女事務委員會主席陳婉嫻，早在八十年代已經活躍於當時男性主導的工會和政圈，在今次訪問中，也少有地提到自己曾經差點結婚的往事。<br />\n「嫻姐」重視民生工作，回想以前在地區事務上，議員和官員可以合作做實事。她和時任發展局局長的林鄭月娥，也曾合作解決啟德明渠問題。她覺得現在的政治氣氛變成怎樣？今晚八點聽她說。<br />\n《鏗鏘說：女中豪傑》<br />\n今晚八點港台電視31<br />\n主持：羅永聰<br />\n#鏗鏘說<br />\n#陳婉嫻<br />\n#羅永聰<br />\n#婦女事務委員會<br />\n#港台電視31<br />\n#逢星期五晚八點"},{"pid":"f7bf022ea911a286f2f8f3724064349c1ae1905f","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"今次訪問呢條撚樣..."},{"pid":"e90529dff8b47a4c1bf8a868ccda3fca09bd80d5","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T12:05:58.000Z","msg":"工賊會"},{"pid":"0ba5aef036f10436d329d1a52faa68cb3ce64330","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"佢真係好天真"},{"pid":"f199a3cad6a29c6ee4d73928be716741057a32d6","tid":2424234,"uid":244357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n聽晚係蘇玉華訪杜琪峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52d83225139e043fc94a294a34d197e0448e191","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"【鏗鏘說】「電影已死？」「UA結業」「咁大件事冇人講？」仍然在拍電影的杜琪峯，不但認為電影未死，更鼓勵年青導演要繼續拍片，困難時間更要用「聰明」的方法面對。杜Sir在訪問中又親自解說，他電影世界中的「隱喻」和「宿命」。今晚八點。<br />\n《鏗鏘說：登峯造極》杜琪峯<br />\n今晚八點港台電視31<br />\n主持：蘇玉華<br />\n#鏗鏘說<br />\n#杜琪峯<br />\n#蘇玉華<br />\n#電影已死<br />\n#鮮浪潮"},{"pid":"2af73070e3d0de6b56eb5469268ad241158ca446","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T16:48:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Id8RguWvjqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FId8RguWvjqM&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2By%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=4b276e91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Id8RguWvjqM</a>"},{"pid":"7c51b1477f9205b98813cac982593a8e7857d24c","tid":2424234,"uid":200165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac3e98d1bdb6cf1573ac491eed069adcd106a72","tid":2424234,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"被稱為「祖堯BB」的前中大校長沈祖堯在訪問中說, 當年和朱咪咪一次上台表演, 令他踏上校長之路。這位「沙士英雄」以往專注在醫學上,做校長令他開拓了新思維。他即將離港,亦期望接受新挑戰。<br />\n《鏗鏘說：瘟疫蔓延時》<br />\n全集重溫：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K3FDCOpMPsQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK3FDCOpMPsQ&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2By%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5